works.description: Bicycling will be an absolute pleasure with the new Folding Bike from the BMW Group’s MINI offshoot. The new MINI Folding Bike, when folded, fits easily and perfectly into the trunk of almost every four-wheeler, making it a great buy for an urban commuter. We know that you love driving your MINI car, but this bike would be a great option when you are visiting places like an overcrowded city center, and the best part will be that you will be still riding a MINI.
